---
title: Smokey Bacon Gnocchi with Broccoli and Mushrooms
description: We think that pan-fried gnocchi is not only super tasty but incredibly easy to make! The gnocchi has a crispy coating and a pillow-like centre, accompanied by ‘meaty’ mushrooms, tasty broccoli, cheese and flat leaf parsley.
